OL,3,CProgramme listings for
OL,3,CProgramme listings for TUE 3 MAR
OL,4,G2100FMy Week With Maggi Hambling
OL,5,     GIn this brand-new encounter with
OL,6,     Gone of our greatest living
OL,7,     Gartists, art historian and
OL,8,     Gcurator Kate Bryan immerses
OL,9,     Gherself in icon Maggi Hambling's
OL,10,     Glife and work.
OL,11,G2200FMy Week With Lubaina Himid
OL,12,     GAn exploration of Himid's life
OL,13,     Gover seven days after the crew
OL,14,     Gdeparts, as Kate captures candid
OL,15,     Gmoments with just an iPhone.
OL,16,G2300FMy Week With Guerrilla Girls
OL,17,     GKate Bryan explores the lives of
OL,18,     Gthe Guerrilla Girls, a group of
OL,19,     Gart activists who haven't granted
OL,20,     Ga film crew full access to their
OL,21,     Glives and work in over 30 years.
