OL,3,CProgramme listings for TUE 3 MAR
OL,4,G0000FThe Black Italian Renaissance
OL,5,     GUncover the untold story of
OL,6,     GAfrican people who lived during
OL,7,     Gthe Italian Renaissance, often
OL,8,     Gappearing in famous paintings
OL,9,     Gonly to be unacknowledged and
OL,10,     Ghidden in plain sight.
OL,11,G0200FLandscape Artist Of The Year 2026
OL,12,     GThe Falkirk Wheel: Stephen Mangan
OL,13,     Ghosts the grand finale with just
OL,14,     Gthree artists who have made it
OL,15,     Gthrough to the last round of the
OL,16,     Gcompetition.
OL,17,G0300FLandscape Artist Of The Year 2026
OL,18,     GWinner's Film: We join the winner
OL,19,     Gof this year's Sky Arts Landscape
OL,20,     GArtist of the Year as they travel
OL,21,     Gto County Mayo to research their
OL,22,     G#10,000 prize commission.
