OL,4,G0400FPlay In A Day
OL,5,     GNew graduates and creative teams
OL,6,     Ghave 24 hours to stage a 15-
OL,7,     Gminute dance show.
OL,8,G0500FAuction
OL,9,     GA rare portrait of two young
OL,10,     Gbrothers by Titian is the
OL,11,     Ghighlight of an Old Masters sale
OL,12,     Gat Sotheby's. Meanwhile at
OL,13,     GChristie's, some Cartier
OL,14,     Gjewellery is being auctioned.
OL,15,G0530FAuction
OL,16,     GA sketch by John Constable is
OL,17,     Gexpected to fetch #300,000 at
OL,18,     GBonhams, while Sotheby's is
OL,19,     Gselling the art collection of
OL,20,     Gmusic legend David Bowie.
